name: Enum Taskbar.Feature
text:
List of provided features. Each platform supports a different
 set of features.  You may use the Taskbar.isSupported(java.awt.Taskbar.Feature)
 method to determine if the given feature is supported by the
 current platform.
codes:
public static enum Taskbar.Feature
extends Enum<Taskbar.Feature>

methods.description:
